				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Di/Bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-WBrUzdsbV27GymPJmmHEMg">Biệt - 別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Di/author-ORfogRLuJo5mkrUrEUhFVA">Từ Di</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Ph%C3%B9ng/Cung-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-jzTq_fmBKdS0V1xxfGB0SA">Cung từ - 宮詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Ph%C3%B9ng/author-2lovo1tul_9ix8CytGMv0Q">Tiết Phùng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/Du-Ph%E1%BA%ADt-T%C3%ADch-s%C6%A1n-ng%E1%BA%ABu-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-ynF4DhG13z2qftelSO6o_Q">Du Phật Tích sơn ngẫu đề - 遊佛跡山偶題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nhi%E1%BA%BFp-Di-Trung/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-thu%E1%BB%B3-th%E1%BB%A7/poem-cqQmmW-FsBPvDcLJsH0X9Q">Đại thuỳ thủ - 大垂手</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nhi%E1%BA%BFp-Di-Trung/author-JPBJfe6mzLjgKnSRDIIASg">Nhiếp Di Trung</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/%C4%90%C3%A1p-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Giang-n%E1%BA%A1p-ng%C3%B4n-b%E1%BB%87nh-trung/poem-2muL3HaT9o2mgNVMEV84Qg">Đáp Lương Giang nạp ngôn bệnh trung - 答梁江納言病中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/author-h_HbFCmxWKkwxboqzaEfNA">Trần Nguyên Đán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Ho%C3%A0ng-H%E1%BA%A1c-l%C3%A2u/poem-12DeuGH-zr92vm-pHvDl_A">Đề Hoàng Hạc lâu - 題黃鶴樓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-phi%E1%BA%BFn-k%E1%BB%B3-01/poem-6jBGADW-lnj_5Syjyfx3vw">Đề phiến kỳ 01 - 題扇其一</a> (<a href="h